[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1152","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1152.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1518","title":"BSD/OS FreeBSD NetBSD Linux 共享内存 mmap/shmget 资源限制绕过拒绝服务漏洞","description":"基于 BSD 4.4 代码实现的共享内存机制（如 mmap 与 shmget 系统调用）存在设计缺陷，本地普通用户可利用其分配大量共享内存并触发页错误（page fault），从而绕过系统设定的资源限制（例如 rlimits 内存上限），耗尽系统内存资源导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响使用 BSD 4.4 共享内存实现的多种操作系统，包括 BSD/OS 4.0、FreeBSD 3.2、NetBSD 1.4 及 Linux 2.3 内核等。攻击条件为攻击者需在目标系统上拥有本地普通用户权限，通过编写并运行特制程序调用 mmap 或 shmget 分配内存即可实施利用，无需远程网络访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1518"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-07-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","remediation":"对于 Linux 系统，建议升级至内核 2.2.12 或更高版本，该版本修复了 mmap 和 shmget 未强制执行 rlimits 的问题。对于 FreeBSD 3.2 系统，应应用 FreeBSD-SA-99:03 安全公告补丁。对于 NetBSD 1.4 系统，应应用 NetBSD-SA1999-006 补丁。临时缓解措施包括：配置 /etc/limits 文件，设置默认虚拟内存限制，并通过 sysctl 限制 System V 共享内存参数（kern.shminfo.shmmax、kern.shminfo.shmall），使用户无法分配超出物理内存的共享内存段。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93207728118694&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/526","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2351","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19423"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1152.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1116","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1116.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1460","title":"BMC Software Patrol SNMP Agent 任意文件创建权限提升漏洞","description":"BMC PATROL SNMP Agent 在 3.2.07 版本之前存在本地权限提升与不安全文件创建漏洞。该漏洞源于其随附的 snmpmagt 程序以 root 权限运行，却未对参数进行充分的权限与路径校验。本地已登录的低权限用户可在执行 snmpmagt 时将目标文件路径作为第二个参数传入，从而以 root 身份在系统中创建任意文件，且所创建文件被设置为全局可写（world-writeable）权限。攻击条件为攻击者需具备目标系统的本地访问权限（无需远程网络可达），并能够执行 snmpmagt 程序。成功利用后，攻击者可借此写入关键系统文件或植入后门，进而实现本地权限提升与持久化控制，影响范围为部署了受影响的 BMC PATROL 3.2.07 之前版本 SNMP Agent 的服务器。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1460"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-07-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:29.277","remediation":"升级 BMC PATROL SNMP Agent 到 3.2.07 或更高版本，这是修复该漏洞的官方安全补丁。如无法立即更新，可通过修改 snmpmagt 配置文件，限制该程序的权限并启用文件审计机制作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93198293132463&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93372579004129&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/525","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19422","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0e46881568ba1d1c2011ec61282a082880cda856/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1460.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1460","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1460.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1460.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j5w8-q6hm-5q59/GHSA-j5w8-q6hm-5q59.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/525/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1460.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--89b0409e-90f4-4b11-9af5-34cb7181ddff.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1116.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0995","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0995.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1166","title":"Linux Kernel 2.0.37 Segment Limit 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.0.37 版本中存在段限制（Segment Limit）编码缺陷漏洞，由于内核未正确编码自定义段限制，导致本地攻击者能够通过访问和修改内核内存来提升权限至 root。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.0.37 版本，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。目前官方已发布更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1166"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.663","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.x 或更高版本，该漏洞在内核 2.0.38 及之后版本中已被修复。由于 2.0.x 系列已停止维护，建议升级至仍受支持的内核分支（如 2.6.x 或更新版本）。如无法升级内核，可通过 grsecurity/PaX 等内核加固补丁限制本地用户访问内核内存空间作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/18156","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/523","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19419","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1166.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1166","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1166.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1166.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8cc4-2w6x-64qg/GHSA-8cc4-2w6x-64qg.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/523/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1166.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75dad3ad336e6258a42cd1ce4af061eea68ed76/cve.files/cveToFile.json.type.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d8e06286-da34-4b52-b892-6e49e4aafd25.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0995.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0995.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0995.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1174","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1174.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1543","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9139,\"outputTokens\":26,\"totalTokens\":10829}}","description":"tags to ensure proper formatting.<value>Apple Mac OS 8 8.6 操作系统中存在密码存储弱加密漏洞，该系统使用弱加密算法存储在用户与用户组数据文件中的密码。攻击者可借此漏洞无需任何身份验证即可访问系统中的用户密码数据，窃取敏感信息。通过暴力破解或密码重放技术，攻击者可以轻易获取受害者密码，进而获得对系统的非法访问权限，对用户隐私安全构成严重威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1543"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-07-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:40.950","remediation":"建议升级到 macOS 10.x 或更高版本，彻底替换已终止支持的 Mac OS 8。当前系统应立即禁用本地用户账户并迁移到现代认证机制。为确保安全性，请启用 FileVault 磁盘加密并使用 Stronger密码策略，修改默认的弱加密算法。如果无法立即升级，请通过安全外设设备限制网络访问，并部署第三方安全软件以监控密码存储区域。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93188174906513&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93736667813924&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/519","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19417","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/49836c1c79a31c6cbe258de560530ef5be1db5f4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1543.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1543","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1543.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/36499b7630ab4a32d11ab7c901b4c87271211bec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1543.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ae10aeb9b17952d60531f6bc06df8547d2b0b568/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4cvf-99qg-vwq4/GHSA-4cvf-99qg-vwq4.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5dbf3673-c284-41c3-937d-5a583aa11b9a.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1543.json","https://github.com/SecurityTapestry-Queen/nvd-cve-api-search/blob/877dddf883cfea2de85c4b40c3c7fb57ce35804a/archive/2025-04-05/report-04-05-2025-21-01-24.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1174.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0574","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0574.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0809","title":"Netscape Communicator 4.x 安全绕过漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.x 在启用 JavaScript 时存在安全绕过漏洞，即使用户设置了\"仅接受来自同一服务器的 cookie\"选项，浏览器也不会对 cookie 设置发出警告。攻击者可通过恶意 JavaScript 代码绕过同源策略限制，在用户不知情的情况下设置或读取跨域 cookie，导致隐私泄露或会话劫持。该漏洞影响 Netscape Communicator 4.x 所有启用 JavaScript 的版本，攻击者需诱导用户访问包含恶意脚本的页面即可触发，CVSS 评分 5.0，属中危漏洞。Netscape 已在后续版本中修复此同源策略绕过问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0809"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.117","remediation":"升级到 Netscape Communicator 4.51 或更高版本以修复该 cookie 安全设置提示缺陷；在无法立即升级时，可在浏览器偏好设置中关闭 JavaScript 功能，或手动将 cookie 接受策略设置为\"仅接受来自同一服务器的 cookie\"，以缓解隐私泄露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0809","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5b55afba6f3a87fe9319e1de76170e4c2760d614/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0809.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0809","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0809.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0809.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h6pv-h65g-hmwg/GHSA-h6pv-h65g-hmwg.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0809.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000692.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0809.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0574.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1171","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1171.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1537","title":"Microsoft IIS 3.0/4.0 SSL资源耗尽拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0/4.0 web服务器存在SSL资源耗尽拒绝服务漏洞。该漏洞源于IIS未能正确区分需要加密传输和无需加密传输的页面，当远程攻击者通过HTTPS端口向原本设计为非加密传输的文件发送SSL请求时，服务器会额外执行SSL加密工作来传输这些文件，从而导致服务器资源被大量消耗。攻击者无需认证，只需持续构造此类SSL请求即可耗尽服务器资源，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响Microsoft IIS 3.x和4.x版本，CVSS评分为5.0，属于中等危害等级，对部署了IIS的Web服务器构成潜在威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1537"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:39.457","remediation":"立即升级 Microsoft IIS 到受支持的版本（至少 IIS 6.0 以上，推荐 IIS 10.0）。IIS 3.0 和 4.0 已于 2004 年终止支持，不再提供安全补丁，应尽快迁移至 Windows Server 2016/2019/2022 搭配的 IIS 10.0。若短期无法升级，可在 IIS 管理器中将需要加密的页面和不需要加密的页面分别绑定到不同的端口或虚拟主机，避免所有站点共用 HTTPS 端口 443；同时通过防火墙限制对 HTTPS 端口的异常高频连接，降低 SSL 资源耗尽风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93138827329577&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/521","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2352","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7427eace1f860911aaff217b01d8aca088243b9f/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1537.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1537","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1537.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3950bef6f70c411ea08c8b2f1665dbd7d38277bd/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1537.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/51a0e15452743e596ced46bb3f156961c52df5bb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-54rf-m93w-vh4v/GHSA-54rf-m93w-vh4v.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1537.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1537.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--55818ba3-d1c2-439f-a985-7ca0986546f4.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/521/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1171.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0509","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0509.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0728","title":"Microsoft Windows NT IOCTL 权限控制不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 操作系统在处理键盘与鼠标的输入输出控制时存在权限校验缺陷，本地已登录的普通用户可绕过系统限制，直接调用内核中控制输入设备的 IOCTL（如用于禁用键盘或鼠标的设备控制码），强制关闭或禁用这些输入设备。该漏洞影响运行 Windows NT 的本地系统，攻击前提是攻击者需在目标主机上拥有合法的交互式登录会话，利用方式为执行特制程序直接下发相应的 IOCTL 请求，使目标主机的键盘或鼠标失去响应，导致本地拒绝服务，干扰正常用户的操作并影响系统可用性。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0728"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.960","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 针对 Windows NT 发布的安全更新补丁，或升级至 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6 及以上版本。如无法立即补丁，可通过修改注册表限制普通用户对键盘和鼠标设备驱动程序的访问权限，将相关 IOCTL 调用权限仅授予管理员账户，或通过组策略禁用非管理员用户的交互式桌面访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ236359","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-024","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0728.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0728","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0728.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d2eb55660fa7a900eec90103b031be5d6f98d9ec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0728.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1dbd44058e428445290bfb1f6fc6ecc0addbfd35/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r7mg-fmm2-chj3/GHSA-r7mg-fmm2-chj3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0728.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0509.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0453","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0453.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0752","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server SSL 握手缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 在处理 SSL 握手过程时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，其根本原因是服务器对 SSL 握手阶段接收的数据缺乏充分的长度校验。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器的 SSL 端口发送特制的、超长的握手数据包，触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃，从而引发拒绝服务。攻击者仅需具备网络可达性即可发起攻击，无需任何凭据或用户交互。该漏洞影响 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6 等版本，成功利用会造成 Web 服务不可用，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0752"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.993","remediation":"建议立即升级 Netscape Enterprise Server 至 3.6.1 或更高安全版本以修复 SSL 握手缓冲区溢出漏洞，或迁移至受支持的 iPlanet Web Server。如暂时无法升级，可在防火墙及反向代理设备上配置规则拦截包含超长记录的畸形 SSL 握手报文作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0752","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19416","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/20b9340dcaffca733259fb153ac741206a5bbc5f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0752.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0752","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0752.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e90735e3e31fc62018265dfbae313d166e653462/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0752.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jq89-jcvx-x6h9/GHSA-jq89-jcvx-x6h9.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0752.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e6bc36b6-8003-41ad-8193-439e990880f9.json","https://github.com/michael1981/sfish_pt/blob/14f609d56e35e9810a1de14712293ab47cc03a46/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%2B%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F%2B%E7%88%86%E7%A0%B4/X-Scan-v3.3/plugins/netscape_crash.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0453.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1127","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1127.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1478","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 Sun Java HotSpot 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun HotSpot Performance Engine VM 存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向运行 HotSpot 的服务器发送包含 \"[\" 字符的特制 URL 触发该漏洞，导致 Java 虚拟机崩溃并造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Microsoft IIS 4.0 等集成 Sun Java HotSpot 的 Web 服务器平台，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。攻击者只需构造简单的恶意 URL 即可实施攻击，无需其他前置条件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1478"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-06","updated":"1999-07-06","remediation":"升级至 Microsoft IIS 5.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，卸载 Sun Java HotSpot Performance Engine 或禁用 IIS 对 Java 的调用。在 IIS 中配置 URL 过滤规则，拦截包含非法字符（如 `[`）的请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58a0ea900decdd7e971b95fcaa99234de5a5df5e/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1478.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1478","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1478.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/dabf5b9888e8885cf125c5729901a7ad84d00092/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1478.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-chqh-vf5r-qvxr/GHSA-chqh-vf5r-qvxr.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1478.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1478.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--44b1a868-b5e3-4dd6-8a6e-aa90eec10ca0.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1127.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1127.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1127.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1097","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1097.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1394","title":"BSD/OS FreeBSD NetBSD OpenBSD UFS Secure Level 1 安全绕过漏洞","description":"基于 BSD 4.4 的多个操作系统（包括 BSDI BSD/OS 4.0、FreeBSD 3.2、NetBSD 1.4 x86 以及 OpenBSD 2.5）在运行于安全级别 1（securelevel 1）时存在 UFS 文件系统保护机制缺陷。系统本应通过 immutable（不可修改）与 append-only（仅追加）标志防止文件被篡改，但拥有 root 权限的本地攻击者可以先卸载目标文件系统，再借助 fsdb 等底层文件系统编辑器直接通过块设备访问并修改磁盘上的文件元数据，从而清除上述保护标志。该漏洞影响所有运行在安全级别 1 的上述 BSD 衍生系统，攻击条件为攻击者需具备本地 root 权限且能卸载文件系统，利用方式是通过设备节点直接编辑文件系统绕过内核级保护，可导致关键系统文件被篡改，危害系统完整性与安全性。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1394"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-07-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:20.763","remediation":"立即将受影响的 BSD 系统升级至已修复该漏洞的版本：BSDI BSD/OS 升级至 4.1 或更高版本，FreeBSD 升级至 3.2-STABLE 或更高版本，NetBSD 升级至 1.4.1 或更高版本，OpenBSD 升级至 2.6 或更高版本。临时缓解措施：将 UFS secure level 从 1 提升至 2，安全级别 2 会禁止 root 清除文件的 immutable 和 append-only 标志，即使通过卸载文件系统并使用 fsdb 等工具直接修改设备也无法绕过。如暂无法立即升级，应通过 sysctl 或内核启动参数将 kern.securelevel 设为 2，并严格限制物理控制台和 root 账户访问权限，防止未授权人员接触单用户模式。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93094058620450&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/510","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19411","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7cda0b7fa75f17f1e2b56ef076a6f9175f854ab4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1394.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1394","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1394.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4cacb08131e7c4736ad136de17873dbcaeddf850/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1394.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f7wg-pwf9-wgf9/GHSA-f7wg-pwf9-wgf9.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/510/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1394.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000688.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/1eac58e77e525b997a47e513089ff82762c04643/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1097.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0308","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0308.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0696","title":"CDE rpc.cmsd 日历管理服务守护进程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"CDE 日历管理器服务守护进程（rpc.cmsd）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求触发该漏洞，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Caldera OpenUnix 8.0、UnixWare 7.1.1、HP HP-UX 11.0、Solaris 7.0 及 SunOS 4.1.4 等多个 UNIX 操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0696"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.067","remediation":"立即安装各厂商提供的安全补丁：HP-UX 11.0 安装 PHCO_20200 或更新版本补丁；Solaris 7.0 安装 106900-07 或更新版本；UnixWare/OpenUnix 安装 Caldera 官方补丁。如无法打补丁，在 inetd.conf 中注释 rpc.cmsd 服务行并重启 inetd 以禁用 CDE 日历管理器服务，或在防火墙层面阻止 TCP 端口 611 的入站访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/188","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-051.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9908-102","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19421","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/553b36786ea28855fe97ba80cc96d54a735075a3/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0696.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0696","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0696.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0f6f0e28732bc614273e91613aef04def1dce90b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0696.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/1907.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2df7e2c20081f44b866b16619f1f9253b790f640/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h3qp-3qwx-3x56/GHSA-h3qp-3qwx-3x56.json","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/4edc9938788d3f7fc2435789a001f306b27788b7/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/1909.txt","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/2011/gb_cde_rpc_cmsd_service_detect.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0308.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0254","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0254.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0690","title":"HP CDE 将当前目录加入 root 的 PATH 环境变量导致权限提升漏洞","description":"HP CDE（Common Desktop Environment）在设置 root 用户环境变量 PATH 时错误地将当前目录 \".\" 包含在内，导致本地攻击者可在任意目录中放置与系统命令同名的恶意程序，当 root 用户通过 su 或登录进入该目录并执行未指定路径的命令时，恶意程序将以 root 权限自动执行，实现本地提权。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 系统中运行 CDE 的版本，需要攻击者拥有本地 shell 访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0690"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.300","remediation":"编辑 root 用户的 .profile、.login 或 CDE 系统级配置文件 /etc/dt/config/Xsession.d/ 下的相关脚本，移除 PATH 中的当前目录（即删除 \".\" 或空路径项），确保 PATH 仅包含绝对路径的系统目录（如 /usr/bin:/usr/sbin）。同时建议修改 CDE 启动脚本中 PATH 的拼接方式，使用完整路径调用命令，消除当前目录隐式搜索带来的提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-053.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9907-100","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0690.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0690","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0690.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0690.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rf75-mr45-vgcx/GHSA-rf75-mr45-vgcx.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_300_400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0690.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-427.txt","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/CWE-Expert/blob/f634e911e6c24a1ad8b9619383e2ab3eb2d9ebd4/CWE_corpus/markdown/4_cwe_trimmed_top25.md.txt","https://github.com/ws-researcher/CAEA/blob/098ddb07c83845feda3d1b1d56ef634927954af4/KGA/dataSet/ICNS/entN_ids_1"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0254.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0248","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0248.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0688","title":"HP 软件分发器 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP-UX 系统的软件分发器（Software Distributor，简称 SD）在 10.x 与 11.x 版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该漏洞源于 SD 组件在处理特定输入时未对数据长度做充分边界校验，导致攻击者可控的过长数据写入固定大小的缓冲区，进而可覆盖相邻内存并可能实现任意代码执行。影响范围为运行 HPUX 10.x 和 11.x 且启用 SD 服务的系统。攻击条件为攻击者需能够向目标系统的 SD 服务发送特制请求，通常需要一定的本地或相邻网络访问权限。利用方式为构造恶意输入触发缓冲区溢出，造成服务异常或提升权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0688"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.047","remediation":"立即安装 HP-UX 11.11 或更高版本的 HP Software Distributor 补丁 HPD4365-11，或者应用 HPSBUX9907-101 安全更新。如需继续使用 HPUX 10.x，请应用 HP SD 10.20 补丁套件。立即更新系统，关闭不必要的 SD 服务以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/545","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9907-101","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0688.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0688","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0688.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0688.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-873q-3c4x-555r/GHSA-873q-3c4x-555r.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0688.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--9b15c9ce-60ad-4d9f-bb76-76ab2ab118a8.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0248.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1065","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1065.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1348","title":"Red Hat Linux Linuxconf 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 6.0 及更早版本中的 Linuxconf 工具未能正确禁用基于 PAM 的 shutdown 命令访问权限，导致本地用户可利用该缺陷直接执行 shutdown 命令，造成系统拒绝服务。该漏洞攻击条件低，本地用户无需特殊权限即可触发，影响 Red Hat Linux 6.0 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1348"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:14.943","remediation":"升级到 Red Hat Linux 6.1 或更高版本，该版本已修复 Linuxconf 对 shutdown 命令的 PAM 访问控制问题。如无法升级，可手动编辑 /etc/pam.d/shutdown 配置文件，移除或注释掉不必要的认证规则，限制仅 root 用户可执行 shutdown 命令。作为临时缓解措施，可通过 chmod 700 /sbin/shutdown 限制 shutdown 二进制文件的执行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93220073515880&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7638326ff3f30ccdb52a67547408dd61f5cdc6cc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1348.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1348","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1348.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1348.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vfvh-4q9r-qw3j/GHSA-vfvh-4q9r-qw3j.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1348.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000685.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ee9754343b23d8c0f998865ae48a5d400d72ba81/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1065.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0508","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0508.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0726","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 图像头处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 系统对可执行文件映像头的校验存在缺陷，攻击者可通过构造恶意的 PE 文件头，诱使用户执行该文件，触发系统内核解析异常，导致目标系统蓝屏崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 版本，攻击者需要诱导用户运行特制程序，无法远程直接利用，CVSS 评分 7.8，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0726"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-06-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.700","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 或更高版本的安全更新，该更新修复了畸形文件映像头导致的拒绝服务问题。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本。如无法升级，可在防火墙层面限制不可信程序执行权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ234557","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/499","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-023","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0726.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d2eb55660fa7a900eec90103b031be5d6f98d9ec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0726.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0726","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0726.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0726.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/7ad5a0b8a6cc847a756fff84ffda27203e470e86/1999/CVE-1999-0726.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/370723f19bf3029ced147d3128d845761f3168c3/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-07xx/CVE-1999-0726.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0726.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0726.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/